= TRADITION

Threats in our lands have been here since the dawn of time; we found shelter in our tradition. Our tradition made us adress theats in a way that is unique to us, and that is what defines us. 

== The Fateful
Fate can be twisted as threats always have more than one side. Playing with this multi-sided world is what makes us unique. 

Mark stress: Alter fate
Restore stress by : Changing a min for a max

=== Alter fate
When dice are rolled, you can mark stress to reroll any number of them.


== The Supported
Fighting against the threats is futile, we decided to fight alongside with them. Exploting threats is what makes us unique.

Mark stress: Convoque Affinity
Restore stress by : Spending time in affinity

=== Convoque Affinity
When you are in presence of an affinited threat, you can mark stress to convoque it into a vessel. The Vessel is an item that turns into a temporary ally and performs predefined actions to help you. 


== The knowledgeable
Understanding threats help us predict them, and even control them. Knowledge is power, and that is what makes us unique. 

Mark Stress: Draw Knowledge
Mark Stress: Apply Knowledge
Restore stress by: Learning something

=== Draw Knowledge
When a situations allows you to draw knowledge, you draft one of the top 3 cards of a (Tarot / Normal) deck and choose one to keep. This card can be expanded to change the outcome of a dice roll. Beware of the number 13.

=== Apply knowledge
When a situation allows you to apply knowledge, you can mark stress and expand you knowledge to automatically succeed at a task
